## Wipeout Analysis
- Root cause: economy death spiral
- Hub starts with 24 of each element, gets consumed by gear purchases
- If hub runs dry before miners deposit, nobody can get gear or hearts
- All agents stuck at hp=0 for entire game
- Fix: economy-gated role assignment + better early survival retreat

## v81 Changes
- Economy-gated pressure budgets:
  - Step 0-60: all miners unless min_res >= 10
  - Step 60-200: gradual ramp (0/2/4 pressure based on min_res)
  - Step 200-3000: 5 pressure (drop to 2 if economy struggling)
  - Step 3000+: 6 pressure (drop to 3 if struggling)
  - Economy thresholds raised from 1 to 3
- Scramblers start at step 200 (was 100)
- Survival retreat more aggressive: triggers at distance 5+ with hp < distance+10
- Testing v81 with seeds 42, 123, 456

